data.description: Welcome Home. Exquisitely Captivating with Unmistakable Style and Contemporary Upgrades! Completely Revamped with Every Modern Amenity. Generous Living Space Perfect for Relaxation. Stunning Kitchen featuring Quartz Countertops, a Cozy Breakfast Bar, Abundant Cabinetry, and Stainless-Steel Appliances. Separate dining room. Five Spacious Bedrooms and Two Full Bathrooms. New Plumbing, Updated Electrical Systems, and Brand-New Flooring! Two new Heat and Air Conditioning Furnaces. Large Backyard, Ideal for all BBQ and Entertainment needs, Complete with a Detached Two-Car Garage. This is the Perfect Place to Call Home in a great location, close to all amenities, schools, parks, and recreation. An Opportunity You Won't Want to Pass Up!
